{"tid":662944,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友成日唔記得我同佢講過嘅嘢","createTime":"2018-05-13T00:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T19:25:53.000Z","uid":164797,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9a9a8f977fdd003e0a34c425bf6e8dc4694bbff7","tid":662944,"uid":164797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:08:46.000Z","msg":"例如我上晝同佢講，我爸媽呢幾日去左旅行，今晚同朋友食飯<br />\n佢完全唔搵我，我夜晚問佢做咩唔搵我，佢話以為我忙緊<br />\n跟住問返我，乜你出左去食咩，做咩唔同屋企人食？<br />\n呢個只係其中一個例子，我發覺佢對我嘅好多嘢都好唔上心，我好唔開心，因為佢講嗰啲嘢我都會記得<br />\n<br />\n我唔想用哭哭鬧鬧嘅方法去同佢講<br />\n想等情緒平復啲先<br />\n有無絲打男朋友都係咁？"},{"pid":"3a648c26146032591030d62d9c8937b5c75450d5","tid":662944,"uid":6245,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:11:29.000Z","msg":"要同時記兩個或以上人既野係難D"},{"pid":"3723c5e771baea8fc83c08ec5449c00899dc5939","tid":662944,"uid":70532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:13:45.000Z","msg":"唉我唔知"},{"pid":"206a50ab6b2bf47611143c50d4cbfc28583554e3","tid":662944,"uid":164797,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a648c26146032591030d62d9c8937b5c75450d5","tid":662944,"uid":6245,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:11:29.000Z","msg":"要同時記兩個或以上人既野係難D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T01:18:16.000Z","msg":"帽事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274771ac85987bcdb9f2c53b20d4d847f1438219","tid":662944,"uid":17502,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"憨鳩，我連我自己朝早食咗乜都唔記得啦，有野就講啦。"},{"pid":"bae9235a85d211ab3efdc1ba2b915015a0331f81","tid":662944,"uid":81575,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9a9a8f977fdd003e0a34c425bf6e8dc4694bbff7","tid":662944,"uid":164797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T00:08:46.000Z","msg":"例如我上晝同佢講，我爸媽呢幾日去左旅行，今晚同朋友食飯<br />\n佢完全唔搵我，我夜晚問佢做咩唔搵我，佢話以為我忙緊<br />\n跟住問返我，乜你出左去食咩，做咩唔同屋企人食？<br />\n呢個只係其中一個例子，我發覺佢對我嘅好多嘢都好唔上心，我好唔開心，因為佢講嗰啲嘢我都會記得<br />\n<br />\n我唔想用哭哭鬧鬧嘅方法去同佢講<br />\n想等情緒平復啲先<br />\n有無絲打男朋友都係咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"屋企人唔係屋企，竟然唔去你屋企爆房，呢個男友無前途。"},{"pid":"8c300a515b22de3d865abbbfc759a14bde5cefec","tid":662944,"uid":120955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274771ac85987bcdb9f2c53b20d4d847f1438219","tid":662944,"uid":17502,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"憨鳩，我連我自己朝早食咗乜都唔記得啦，有野就講啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"我連尋晚老母同我講佢今晚唔煮飯都唔記得😑"},{"pid":"f8bba69ff8a3c113c895d032841b728665466b6f","tid":662944,"uid":172684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"你不如試下同佢講<br />\n<br />\n你不如今晚上嚟我屋企 我屋企冇人<br />\n<br />\n如果佢咁都唔記得就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97c3b926437308f3b534e62f7526f9865af016f","tid":662944,"uid":129729,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:37:15.000Z","msg":"我男朋友都係咁<br />\n有次本身壓力已經好大再加埋呢件事忍唔住喊左出黎 佢後尾好似都有唔開心 <br />\n我成日都會諗係唔係因為佢唔夠鍾意我先會咁<br />\n不過算啦 其實我都知樣樣野要記得曬係好難既<br />\n自己要睇開啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9b068425290c6f8393e26265d7f8e37d6b4151","tid":662944,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"用下碌鳩教訓下佢"},{"pid":"e8514e01e476be5f56ec5da93262aea2ce6f328d","tid":662944,"uid":169574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"已經睇到好化 習慣左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356501c5b71ba6e812502909ee8b3aef41627a11","tid":662944,"uid":20867,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"悲觀的人：<br />\n預設對方記住<br />\n會因為對方無心裝載而失望<br />\n<br />\n樂觀的人：<br />\n預設對方忘記<br />\n會因為對方有心裝載而驚喜"},{"pid":"33b59f0f1e3bafafd0e3a603306dd66fa260fe08","tid":662944,"uid":51525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"你想要個個係秘書黎喎"},{"pid":"f42354c1d8b8fe18a714dbc38a87e552c7fec80b","tid":662944,"uid":185960,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"其實無問題，唔需要咁敏感<br />\n<br />\n我對我男朋友好上心<br />\n但係我一樣<br />\n唔記得佢幾時放假<br />\n唔記得佢幾時返夜<br />\n唔記得佢星期幾練波<br />\n唔記得佢比賽係邊度<br />\n前前後後問幾次，最後都唔記得<br />\n<br />\n真係好小事 🐖🐖🐖"},{"pid":"dc2a91529d571f51e8eafbf3979572e8e752939e","tid":662944,"uid":116688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"心靈脆弱成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222ed561383b3c4beba3a8ad073df5d9bc9c857c","tid":662944,"uid":72785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"356501c5b71ba6e812502909ee8b3aef41627a11","tid":662944,"uid":20867,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"悲觀的人：<br />\n預設對方記住<br />\n會因為對方無心裝載而失望<br />\n<br />\n樂觀的人：<br />\n預設對方忘記<br />\n會因為對方有心裝載而驚喜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"應該係掉番轉"},{"pid":"e4b91dd33bf26c76d0ad0be91e21d5ed4c8afefd","tid":662944,"uid":54938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"你都可以唔記得自己有男朋友"},{"pid":"17feed2f7604a78ba4199b10903430882a6995fa","tid":662944,"uid":125557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"以前都成日唔記得佢幾時放假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27b19ac5caef4909d5a19468b067efdaba024f0","tid":662944,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"43b2bc9797b0d00dc8467333c48c206c8d59a6e7","tid":662944,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>悲觀的人：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">期望盡善盡美</span><br />\n預設對方記住<br />\n會因為對方無心裝載而失望<br />\n<br />\n樂觀的人：<br 